data.description: Charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath lovely home nestled in the sought-after Southern Hills neighborhood. This inviting home boasts spacious interiors, perfect for comfortable living and entertaining. As you enter the home you see the spacious living room and move into the dining and large kitchen with a nice kitchen island and updated kitchen appliances. This kitchen is a cooks delight and perfect for making delicious meals and entertaining your friends and family. Features a private 4th bedroom that could be a game room or study. Enjoy the tranquility of a large fenced-in backyard with patio, offering privacy and ample space for outdoor activities or relaxing after a long day. Experience the blend of convenience and serenity in this delightful neighborhood setting. Located across from Southern Hills park with lovely jogging trails, playground as well as other amenities and located near shopping and favorite restaurants. Call your favorite realtor today to set up your private showing.
